description: This file defines a utility function for fetching live data in a frontend application. Currently, the function is a placeholder that throws an error indicating that live data mode is not configured, in accordance with BRD requirements. It is intended to be integrated with a backend data provider in the future.

methods.name: fetchLiveUniverse()
methods.description: An asynchronous function that attempts to fetch live universe data but currently throws an error indicating lack of configuration.
